a-oversight-board-removed-视频-israel-hamas-conflict&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/19/24007655/meta-oversight-board-removed-videos-israel-hamas-conflict" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/19/24007655/meta-oversight-board-removed-videos-israel-hamas-conflict</id><author><name>杰西韦瑟贝德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-19T10:00:00-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-19T10:00:00-05:00</updated><title>为什么 Flexport 首席执行官 Ryan Petersen 收回了他的公司</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Ryan Petersen 对着镜头微笑&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/nYyiXbzwRm8-9QzW23CLR8SmkiU=/0x0:3000x2000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/ uploads/chorus_image/image/72978386/DCD_1219.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;插图由 The Verge 提供 |摄影：Flexport&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;他的继任者上任不到一年就上任了。是什么让彼得森&lt;strong>; &lt;/strong>;回来了？&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24006936/flexport-ceo-ryan-petersen-logistics-fired-dave- clark-return-decoder&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24006936/flexport-ceo-ryan-petersen-logistics-fired-dave-clark-return-decoder" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24006936/flexport-ceo-ryan-petersen-logistics-fired-dave-clark-return-decoder</id><author><name>尼莱·帕特尔</name></author></entry></feed>